        public boolean verifyInterviewer(java.lang.String interviewId,
                        java.lang.String interviewUsername)
        check the interviewer's verification when logging in and assign the attributes.
        Parameters:
        interviewId - Id of the interviewer who is trying to login to the system.
        interviewUsername - User name of the interviewer.
        Returns:

      • createSurveyMessage

        public java.lang.String createSurveyMessage(java.lang.String inviteeId,
                                   java.lang.String surveyId)
        Creates an interview survey message in the table of survey_message_use before starting the interview.
        Parameters:
        inviteeId - Invitee ID for whom the message has to be created.
        surveyId - Survey ID to whom the invitee is linked to.
        Returns:
        String message ID is returned which is used for making the URL for the invitee to access the system
